# Module installation

Follow the guide

## Setting up modulefiles

### Intel compiler

Note: Very hard to do by hand and similarly dangerous as this will not accomodate for other stuff.

First! 

Initializie

source /opt/intel/bin/compilervars.sh intel64

Next 

perl env2 -from bash -to modulecmd "/opt/intel/bin/compilervars.sh intel64" >> my_module_file

This get all the append, preppend you need for the read module file. 


